content.p: FOR STAFF If you need any support with your booking, please email room bookings FOR STUDENTS If you book a room using the 'book a classroom or computer room for study' tile, the following restrictions apply: If you need to book a room outside of these restrictions, you will need to ask a staff member in your school to book it for you e.g. personal tutor, lecturer etc. CONFERENCE BOOKINGS If you require a booking for a conference, please contact Nottingham venues to book one of their venues. Resource Booker - find the room and capacity that meets your needs Resource Booker includes some abbreviated building codes. If you are unsure about the meaning of any of these, our zoning information may help Estates help desk IT Service help desk
